article.description: — David Collins registered 16 points as South Florida got past East Carolina 69-63 on Saturday.
article.headline: South Florida beats East Carolina 69-63
article.story: GREENVILLE, N.C. -- — David Collins registered 16 points as South Florida got past East Carolina 69-63 on Saturday. Justin Brown had 12 points for South Florida (7-5, 3-3 American Athletic Conference). Alexis Yetna added 10 points. Tremont Robinson-White scored a career-high 29 points for the Pirates (7-3, 1-3). Jayden Gardner added 10 points and 10 rebounds. Bitumba Baruti had eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
